  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1223880/" class="title-link">是作者的错还是翻译的错?</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1223880"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/treesky/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/treesky/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">[已注销]</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-10-16"
      class="main-meta">2007-10-16 15:14:34</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1223880_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  看了半天,不知道说啥.. 语句不连惯,通篇都十分生硬..就像一个病人拉的屎.. 不懂法文,不好妄言,但按理来说,拉波特不应该是这个水平的... 敢开言写屎的人,必定有料吃下去才是,若拉不出一些有意义之字,何以能服人也?又何以能让商务出这套所谓的&#34;当代法国思想文化译丛&#34;...这套书除...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1223880/#comments">(5回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 0没用</span>
